OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FTrump threatened Iran and taunts
OL,7,FDemocrats in record-length State of
OL,8,Fthe Union address
OL,10,FThis was more like watching a game
OL,11,Fshow host than a US leader.
OL,13,FPresident Donald Trump was in his
OL,14,Felement at the State of the Union
OL,15,Fspeech, lapping up the theatre of the
OL,16,Foccasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
