CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772025561
OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FIt was difficult to grasp from the
OL,7,Fperformance that Trump may be about to
OL,8,Fbomb Iran or that half of Americans
OL,9,Fregard him as a grave threat to
OL,10,Fdemocracy.
OL,12,FBrilliantly choreographed, he
OL,13,Fpunctuated the speech by highlighting
OL,14,Fthose he regards as true American
OL,15,Fpatriots.
OL,17,FHe brought members of the gold medal-
OL,18,Fwinning US Olympic ice hockey team
OL,19,Finto the House gallery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
