OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FChants of "USA! USA!" echoed around
OL,7,Fthe chamber.
OL,9,FHe also gave the Medal of Honour to
OL,10,Fthe wounded helicopter pilot who led
OL,11,Fthe audacious military raid that
OL,12,Fcaptured the Venezuelan dictator,
OL,13,FNicolas Maduro.
OL,15,FThe political aim last night was clear.
OL,17,FAfter a dramatic and wildly
OL,18,Funpredictable first year of his second
OL,19,Fterm, Trump is trying to reset his
OL,20,Fpresidency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
