OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FThe White House knows it must persuade
OL,7,FAmericans that the country is on the
OL,8,Fright track.
OL,10,FThere is grave political peril ahead
OL,11,Ffor the Trump presidency because there
OL,12,Fare midterm Congressional elections in
OL,13,FNovember that could witness a major
OL,14,Fdefeat for Republicans.
OL,16,FOn tariffs, Trump told Congress he had
OL,17,Ffound another legal framework to keep
OL,18,Fthem in place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
