OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FUnamused, Supreme Court Justices
OL,7,Fwatched on, just days after they had
OL,8,Frejected his tariff policies as
OL,9,Fillegal.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FOn foreign policy, Trump was
OL,17,Fsurprisingly conciliatory - even
OL,18,Fpraising NATO members as "our friends
OL,19,Fand allies".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
