OL,3,CGameshow Trump makes his pitch to
OL,4,Cmidterm voters
OL,6,FTo confront Iran, a huge armada has
OL,7,Fbeen assembled, but despite the
OL,8,Ffirepower and much speculation, Trump
OL,9,Fmade no suggestion that an attack on
OL,10,FIran is imminent.
OL,12,FBut even as Trump celebrated what he
OL,13,Fcalls a "Golden Age," Democrats are
OL,14,Fderiding this as a delusional speech.
OL,16,FWho is right? The real verdict on
OL,17,FTrump's speech - and on his presidency
OL,18,F- will be delivered by American voters
OL,19,Fin November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
